<h1 class="heading-xlarge">Upgrade your account</h1>
<div class="column-two-thirds">
    <p>The Next-Day service is for pre-registered businesses only, who have a genuine business need for regular access to a next-day legalisation service.</p>
    <p>If you're applying on behalf of a business and want to use this service, <a href="<%= user_data.url%>/request-business-service-access?from=account">request Next-Day service access</a>.</p>

    <p>If you aren't applying on behalf of a business, use the <a href="/new-application?app_type_group=1">standard service</a> instead.</p>
</div>
